702646f-b.title: Brooklyn: 21st Street (East) - Kenmore Terrace
702646f-b.text:
East 21st Street, east side, at the N.E. cerner of Eenmuere Terraee,
showing a view ef a frawe house, belengiwp te the Datch Referned Church ef
Flatbush.
Awsst 7, 1931.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, showing the Parsonage of the Dutch Reformed Church of
Flatbush.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(3)
The same, another view.
April, 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
